{"tid":1768490,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"真理褲妹超軟Q 「真人夾娃娃」實境秀鑽洞偷竊","createTime":"2019-12-04T05:49:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-04T10:04:22.000Z","uid":32511,"like":105,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"02d986ba18eef6736c276bcb4e1c95bdce1f4f93","tid":1768490,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T05:49:43.000Z","msg":"新北市三重區仁政街某夾娃娃店，昨天凌晨出現1名身穿真理褲的年輕女子，身體超軟Q，整個人竟從取物洞口鑽進夾娃娃機，偷走2個大型娃娃，警方事後循線查獲22歲李姓女子，她走進派出所時卻突然軟腳，差點跌倒。<br />\n <br />\n據了解，店家昨天發現機台洞口疑遭破壞，調閱監視器看見當天凌晨2時許，有1名身穿真理褲年輕女子，先在店內徘徊許久，離開後約隔30分鐘又返回行竊。<br />\n <br />\n該女趁四下無人，竟從取物洞口扭動160公分身軀鑽入，整個人全部擠進狹窄取物管道，伸手抓了2支大型娃娃，又扭扭扭擠出洞口，拎著娃娃逃離，宛如上演真人夾娃娃實境秀。<br />\n <br />\n警方昨天中午在網路上發現竊案訊息，主動聯繫被害店家瞭解案情，完成報案手續，並調閱監視器循線調查，發現竊嫌步行回家，當天晚間7時54分前往李女住處，當場發現失竊的2個布偶，她也坦承行竊，帶回偵詢後依竊盜罪嫌函送地檢署偵辦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PrZKdxJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPrZKdxJ.jpg&h=a01281ae&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jFZeAL5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjFZeAL5.jpg&h=6500e69f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c1FUAL7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc1FUAL7.jpg&h=6f8c8f1f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZNuFwjt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZNuFwjt.jpg&h=903f173c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C3ZNVMa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC3ZNVMa.jpg&h=0731d5ed&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pZEBO6b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpZEBO6b.jpg&h=0ab474b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"72b062589c7608c94402c5f66e11580f9fea4bb7","tid":1768490,"uid":186844,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T05:52:57.000Z","msg":"已射 thx"},{"pid":"c46895de5202c28bb6115650c5b28bf8387b1621","tid":1768490,"uid":6845,"like":12,"dislike":0,"